      "description": "Check out this reliable daily driver! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid and dependable choice for anyone looking for a practical vehicle. It's in fair condition, meaning it\u2019s well-loved and ready for many more miles, making it a great value for the price!",
