    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition, offering a reliable driving experience for those who prioritize function over form. While the engine and transmission are solid and ready for daily use, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor paint fading on the roof, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows signs of wear, and the air conditioning takes a moment to reach full cooling capacity. It\u2019s a dependable workhorse that has been maintained mechanically but possesses the character marks of a well-used car.",
