      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine currently has significant performance issues and will likely require a major overhaul or replacement to be reliably roadworthy. Externally, the body shows considerable wear, including several deep scratches, noticeable dents, and areas of rust. The interior is also in rough shape, with visible tears in the upholstery and some non-functional electronics. Please be aware that this car will need substantial work and likely a tow to its new destination.",
