      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a brand new home! This car has been super reliable and is a total joy to drive. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it\u2019s in really solid shape for its next owner. Perfect for daily commutes or those fun weekend road trips! It\u2019s clean, dependable, and ready to hit the road today. Shoot me a message if you want to come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
