    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. Critical maintenance is up to date, including addressed rod bearings and a serviced VANOS system to ensure variable valve timing precision. The chassis is reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points and features a limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its age, the suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded bushings and dampers, offering the communicative steering and balanced handling these M-cars are known for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
