    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for, reliable driver. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy shine, showing only the minor, inevitable stone chips consistent with responsible road use. All body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are in excellent shape. Moving inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has been kept smoke-free; the upholstery is supple with no tears, and the dashboard remains free of cracks or sun damage. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is in great health, benefiting from a documented history of timely oil changes and preventative maintenance. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension provides a quiet, composed ride. It\u2019s a complete package that offers a premium driving experience without the 'new car' depreciation.",
